843
00:54:14,240 --> 00:54:16,160
I’ll just assume you’re dead.

844
00:54:16,240 --> 00:54:17,440
And don’t come see me again.

845
00:54:17,960 --> 00:54:19,360
I’m sorry.

846
00:54:19,360 --> 00:54:20,960
Give me another chance, Si.

847
00:54:21,000 --> 00:54:23,440
-What are you even saying.
-We just had bad timing, didn’t we.

848
00:54:23,720 --> 00:54:26,720
-I tried to reach you.
-Jane.

849
00:54:26,920 --> 00:54:27,920
Security.

850
00:54:27,960 --> 00:54:29,000
Security.

851
00:54:32,080 --> 00:54:34,080
I won’t let you leave me.

852
00:54:34,320 --> 00:54:35,360
Try me.

853
00:55:49,400 --> 00:55:50,920
Whatever happens, happens.

854
00:56:14,160 --> 00:56:15,480
How do I even get in.

855
00:56:39,720 --> 00:56:40,640
Hey.

856
00:56:48,440 --> 00:56:49,960
You scared me.

857
00:56:51,760 --> 00:56:52,800
You’re not asleep yet.

858
00:56:53,320 --> 00:56:56,000
I saw you on the CCTV.

859
00:56:56,080 --> 00:56:57,360
Why didn’t you tell me you were coming.

860
00:56:58,240 --> 00:57:00,320
I didn’t plan to come.

861
00:57:00,760 --> 00:57:03,040
It was late, so I thought you were asleep.

862
00:57:03,080 --> 00:57:04,200
So I didn’t call you.

863
00:57:05,800 --> 00:57:07,000
Turn off the engine for me.

864
00:57:07,040 --> 00:57:08,240
I’ll go check on Pao first.

865
00:57:27,760 --> 00:57:29,000
Usually.

866
00:57:29,640 --> 00:57:31,760
Do you sleep with Pao every night.

867
00:57:32,880 --> 00:57:34,240
Not every night.

868
00:57:34,400 --> 00:57:36,600
If I want a peaceful night.

869
00:57:36,960 --> 00:57:38,920
I let her sleep in another room.

870
00:57:45,640 --> 00:57:46,920
Then...

871
00:57:50,040 --> 00:57:52,560
Can she sleep in another room tonight.

872
00:57:56,000 --> 00:57:57,440
Yeah, sure.

873
00:57:59,280 --> 00:58:01,000
Good night, chubby.

874
00:58:14,720 --> 00:58:15,720
What about you.

875
00:58:17,560 --> 00:58:19,120
Is something wrong.

876
00:58:20,640 --> 00:58:22,840
You can tell me anything.

877
00:58:25,400 --> 00:58:27,160
You don’t have to be scared.

878
00:58:28,640 --> 00:58:31,840
Because I want to be your comfort.

879
00:58:43,520 --> 00:58:45,000
Have you...

880
00:58:46,080 --> 00:58:48,640
ever had any naughty thoughts about me.

881
00:58:52,720 --> 00:58:54,040
I don’t mean.

882
00:58:54,040 --> 00:58:56,080
hurting me physically or emotionally.

883
00:58:57,600 --> 00:58:58,640
Then...

884
00:58:59,280 --> 00:59:00,560
what do you mean.

885
00:59:02,880 --> 00:59:05,400
Do you really not know or are you pretending.

886
00:59:11,000 --> 00:59:12,080
Well...

887
00:59:13,280 --> 00:59:15,200
maybe I do, but...

888
00:59:15,800 --> 00:59:17,280
I’m not sure.

889
00:59:30,800 --> 00:59:31,840
So...

890
00:59:32,480 --> 00:59:33,960
what’s your answer.

891
00:59:35,240 --> 00:59:37,760
Have you ever had naughty thoughts about me.

892
00:59:40,760 --> 00:59:42,040
Right now...

893
00:59:43,760 --> 00:59:45,280
I’m having them.

894
00:59:48,880 --> 00:59:49,960
What do you think.

895
00:59:50,000 --> 00:59:52,640
if the two of us really dated.

896
00:59:54,480 --> 00:59:56,080
Do you think it would work.

897
00:59:58,040 --> 00:59:59,040
Well...

898
00:59:59,560 --> 01:00:01,000
it’s hard to say.

899
01:00:01,520 --> 01:00:03,560
But I do hope...

900
01:00:03,800 --> 01:00:05,360
we can make it work.

901
01:00:13,040 --> 01:00:14,560
What if.

902
01:00:16,520 --> 01:00:19,880
I have a past full of mistakes.

903
01:00:20,960 --> 01:00:22,640
Can you accept that.

904
01:00:25,480 --> 01:00:28,080
Who hasn’t made mistakes.

905
01:00:30,880 --> 01:00:32,800
The point is.

906
01:00:33,560 --> 01:00:34,840
if you were wrong.

907
01:00:35,160 --> 01:00:38,160
are you willing to fix it.

908
01:01:05,720 --> 01:01:07,320
I’m sorry.

909
01:01:40,800 --> 01:01:42,040
Do you...

910
01:01:42,560 --> 01:01:44,600
like it when I do this.

911
01:02:39,800 --> 01:02:41,480
Can you not do this.

912
01:02:44,680 --> 01:02:47,000
I don’t want you to get mad.

913
01:02:50,360 --> 01:02:51,560
Besides.

914
01:02:52,360 --> 01:02:53,600
I...

915
01:02:53,760 --> 01:02:55,680
can’t hold back either.

916
01:04:18,760 --> 01:04:19,960
Do you like it.

917
01:04:23,960 --> 01:04:25,680
I love it.

918
01:05:34,240 --> 01:05:36,280
Stop pouting.

919
01:05:36,640 --> 01:05:38,400
It’s making me lose confidence.

920
01:05:40,080 --> 01:05:41,680
Lose confidence about what.

921
01:05:42,160 --> 01:05:43,240
Well...

922
01:05:43,560 --> 01:05:45,240
I’m afraid.

923
01:05:45,320 --> 01:05:48,800
I might not be good enough for you.

924
01:05:49,160 --> 01:05:50,280
Or...

925
01:05:50,680 --> 01:05:52,320
you might not be happy.

926
01:06:01,520 --> 01:06:02,920
You’re really good.

927
01:06:03,600 --> 01:06:05,440
I’m so happy.

928
01:06:21,160 --> 01:06:22,160
Khun Si.

929
01:06:24,880 --> 01:06:26,000
I...

930
01:06:27,480 --> 01:06:30,360
want you to be my life partner.

931
01:06:38,120 --> 01:06:39,560
Will you marry me.

932
01:06:42,080 --> 01:06:43,840
You’re proposing right now.

933
01:06:44,520 --> 01:06:45,520
Yeah.

934
01:07:32,160 --> 01:07:34,840
Why are you here so early? It’s not even 7 yet.

935
01:07:34,880 --> 01:07:37,720
Well, you told me to come early this morning.

936
01:07:40,080 --> 01:07:44,160
I feel like you’re right here in front of me.

937
01:07:44,160 --> 01:07:47,560
Wait… are you about to—?

938
01:07:48,120 --> 01:07:48,840
Yeah.

939
01:07:49,600 --> 01:07:51,320
You’re slaying!

940
01:07:51,320 --> 01:07:53,160
You should dress like this more often.

941
01:07:53,160 --> 01:07:55,600
Dressed like this, even Pidpee and Muedmon would come chasing after

942
01:07:55,600 --> 01:07:57,920
I keep telling you—we’re already broken up.

943
01:07:57,920 --> 01:07:59,400
If you want to break up, go ahead and do it alone.

944
01:07:59,400 --> 01:08:01,480
You really look like my ex.

945
01:08:01,480 --> 01:08:03,840
Seeing you just reminds me of her.

946
01:08:03,840 --> 01:08:05,680
Can I hug you for a second?

947
01:08:05,840 --> 01:08:06,760
Hey!!

948
01:08:06,760 --> 01:08:08,000
Was it fun climbing the wall.

949
01:08:08,040 --> 01:08:09,960
So much fun.

950
01:08:10,000 --> 01:08:11,840
-You always find something to do.
-Put this on the front.

951
01:08:11,880 --> 01:08:13,240
Action.

952
01:08:15,200 --> 01:08:18,479
-Hold on tight, tight around the waist.
-Yes, yes.

953
01:08:18,520 --> 01:08:20,800
-Yes, the waist, yes.
-Good skills.

954
01:08:20,960 --> 01:08:22,479
I said hold the waist.

955
01:08:22,720 --> 01:08:24,240
(This is your specialty.)

956
01:08:26,040 --> 01:08:27,920
-Cut, can we do it again.
-What is it.

957
01:08:27,960 --> 01:08:30,680
-Okay, sound camera.
-Pull it harder.

958
01:08:31,880 --> 01:08:34,760
(This time, extra sweet.)

959
01:08:36,880 --> 01:08:39,160
-Cut, that’s good.
-Cut.
